  "pageTitle": "回收设备购买者的资源库",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"resources-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">资源</p>\n        <h1 id=\"resources-title\">回收设备购买者的资源库</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">在比较WEI LAN回收设备系统或申请提案前，请浏览文件 详情、规划指南、常见问题解答和RFQ准备资源。</p>\n        <nav class=\"resource-category-nav\" aria-label=\"资源类别\">\n          <a href=\"#resource-library\">全部</a>\n          <a href=\"#resource-library\">宣传册</a>\n          <a href=\"#planning-checklist-title\">清单</a>\n          <a href=\"#resource-faq-title\">常见问题</a>\n          <a href=\"#future-guides-title\">向导</a>\n          <a href=\"/resources/maintenance-guide\">维护</a>\n        </nav>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section resources-section\" id=\"resource-library\" aria-labelledby=\"resource-library-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">资源库</p>\n          <h2 id=\"resource-library-title\">资源文章与文献</h2>\n          <p>每个资源现在都有一个 详情 页面，方便海外买家了解文件涵盖的内容、何时使用以及它如何与项目评估相关。</p>\n        </div>\n        <article class=\"resource-featured\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">精选资源</p>\n            <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">项目调查清单</a></h3>\n            <p>在请求设备配置建议前，请准备好废物类型、容量、场地限制、材料照片或视频、输出需求和项目阶段。</p>\n            <div class=\"resource-meta-row\" aria-label=\"精选资源元数据\">\n              <span>清单</span>\n              <span>更新2026-06-30</span>\n              <span>最适合RFQ准备</span>\n            </div>\n            <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">阅读更多</a>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <div class=\"resource-library-list\">\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">公司 / 更新2026-06-30 / 8 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/company-profile\">公司简介</a></h3>\n              <p>WEI LAN定位、制造重点、产品范围及环境技术资质概览。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/company-profile\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">宣传册 / 塑料分类 / 10 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/ai-optical-sorting-system-brochure\">AI 光学分拣系统宣传册</a></h3>\n              <p>物料类别、分拣范围、吞吐量范围、占地面积及可回收塑料项目的使用场景。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/ai-optical-sorting-system-brochure\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">宣传册 / 停止与终止废弃物 / 10 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/construction-waste-recycling-line-brochure\">建筑废物回收线路宣传册</a></h3>\n              <p>集成工艺模块、容量选项、产出目标及C&amp;D回收设施的部署价值。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/construction-waste-recycling-line-brochure\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">规格 / 工程评测 / 12 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">产品规格表</a></h3>\n              <p>光学分拣模型和Lion One集成站点配置的核心参数。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">案例PDF / 参考文献综述 / 9 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/case-study-pdf\">案例研究PDF</a></h3>\n              <p>参考项目概述及技术基准测试和内部流通的典型配置说明。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/case-study-pdf\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">清单 / RFQ准备 / 7 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">项目调查清单</a></h3>\n              <p>分享废弃物类型、国家、容量、场地面积和自动化预期，以便工程部门更快提供建议。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-library-card\">\n            <div class=\"resource-library-card-body\">\n              <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">维护 / 操作 支持 / 8 min</p>\n              <h3><a class=\"resource-title-link\" href=\"/resources/maintenance-guide\">维护指南</a></h3>\n              <p>例行检查、备件、操作员笔记以及长期运行回收设备运行的维护规划主题。</p>\n              <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/maintenance-guide\">阅读更多</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" aria-labelledby=\"planning-checklist-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ准备</p>\n          <h2 id=\"planning-checklist-title\">项目规划清单，以加快提案</h2>\n          <p>完整的项目输入帮助工程部门审查废物成分、容量预期、场地限制及最合适设备路径。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-checklist-grid resource-planning-flow\">\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">01</span>\n            <h3>废物类型与成分</h3>\n            <p>PET瓶子、HDPE、PP、混合塑料、C&D 废弃物、装饰废弃物、拆除废弃物、大块废弃物或混合本地溪流。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">复习检查清单字段</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">02</span>\n            <h3>目标容量</h3>\n            <p>预计每小时的运输吨数、每天的运营时间、旺季变化以及未来的扩展预期。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">比较规格范围</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">03</span>\n            <h3>国家及场地覆盖范围</h3>\n            <p>项目国家、可用可调节车间或场区、电压条件、安装限制及本地交付条件aint。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/contact\">发送站点条件</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">04</span>\n            <h3>期望产积</h3>\n            <p>分类塑料、回收骨料、金属、轻质材料、打包可回收溪流或报告要求。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/construction-waste-recycling-line-brochure\">检查输出示例</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">05</span>\n            <h3>资料照片或视频</h3>\n            <p>如果可以，分享收到的材料照片、视频、污染 详情，以及当前的手动或机械分拣流程。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/contact\">附加材料介质</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">06</span>\n            <h3>项目阶段及文档需求</h3>\n            <p>说明该项目是研究、预算 审批、招标、工厂对比、设备更换还是报价。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">从RFQ清单开始</a>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-planning-action\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"resource-entry-meta\">下一步 / RFQ准备</p>\n            <h3>从RFQ清单开始</h3>\n            <p>在将材料发送给WEI LAN之前，先将清单作为项目简报。它将上述静态输入转化为第一条工程评审路径。</p>\n          </div>\n          <a class=\"resource-read-more\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">开放清单</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section dark-section\" aria-labelledby=\"resource-value-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">团队如何使用它们</p>\n          <h2 id=\"resource-value-title\">文档包应有助于决策的推进</h2>\n          <p>对于国际B2B设备购买，资源不是装饰品。它们帮助商业、工程和管理利益相关者在报价前达成相同的基本理解。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-use-path\">\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">01</span>\n            <h3>比较 供应商 范围</h3>\n            <p>利用宣传册和参数表比较 供应商 的工艺范围、容量范围和部署适配度。</p>\n            <div class=\"resource-path-link-group\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/company-profile\">公司简介</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">规格表</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">02</span>\n            <h3>内部可行性审查</h3>\n            <p>在安排电话会议前，请与业主、EPC合作伙伴或管理层分享公司简介和参考摘要。</p>\n            <div class=\"resource-path-link-group\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/case-study-pdf\">案例研究PDF</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/case-studies\">参考项目</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">03</span>\n            <h3>RFQ准备</h3>\n            <p>咨询清单帮助买方提交更完整的技术意见，从而指导更好的提案方向。</p>\n            <div class=\"resource-path-link-group\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">RFQ清单</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/contact\">发送 项目 详情</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"number\">04</span>\n            <h3>较短的销售周期</h3>\n            <p>当合适的文件及早准备好时，技术讨论可以更快地从发现阶段到推荐阶段。</p>\n            <div class=\"resource-path-link-group\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/ai-optical-sorting-system-brochure\">AI分拣手册</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/maintenance-guide\">维护指南</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section service-section\" aria-labelledby=\"resource-faq-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">常见问题</p>\n          <h2 id=\"resource-faq-title\">这些问题通常在报价请求前会出现</h2>\n          <p>常见问题内容 支持 回答了买家转化和 SEO，回答了通用的 供应商 问题、塑料分类问题和C&D 废弃物项目问题。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-faq-group-grid\">\n          <article class=\"resource-faq-group\">\n            <h3>通用常见问题</h3>\n            <dl>\n              <div>\n                <dt>报价需要哪些信息？</dt>\n                <dd>废弃物类型、目标容量、国家、场地面积、项目阶段和预期产出通常足以引发更准确的讨论。</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>WEI LAN可以自定义系统吗？</dt>\n                <dd>系统方向可根据材料成分、所需纯度、占地、电压、自动化期望和输出目标进行调整。</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <div class=\"resource-faq-actions\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">开放RFQ清单</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/contact\">发送 项目 详情</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-faq-group\">\n            <h3>塑料分拣常见问题</h3>\n            <dl>\n              <div>\n                <dt>哪些塑料材料可以被评估？</dt>\n                <dd>典型材料包括透明PET、绿色PET、蓝色PET、混合色PET、白色HDPE、PP和混合可回收塑料。</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>什么因素会影响分选配置？</dt>\n                <dd>材料比例、污染程度、颜色类别、目标纯度、进料稳定性和自动化要求都会影响推荐的光学分选设置。</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <div class=\"resource-faq-actions\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/ai-optical-sorting-system-brochure\">阅读分拣手册</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/product-specification-sheet\">请查看产品规格</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"resource-faq-group\">\n            <h3>建筑与大件废弃物常见问题解答</h3>\n            <dl>\n              <div>\n                <dt>哪些废弃物流可以讨论？</dt>\n                <dd>C&D 废弃物、装饰废料、拆除废料、大块废料、混合砂和骨料材料、木材、塑料、纺织品和金属都可以被审查。</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>哪些输出应该早期定义？</dt>\n                <dd>买家应定义回收骨料、砂或细粉、金属、轻质材料、打包可回收物及任何本地验收要求。</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <div class=\"resource-faq-actions\">\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/construction-waste-recycling-line-brochure\">阅读C&amp;D宣传册</a>\n              <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/case-study-pdf\">审阅案例PDF</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" aria-labelledby=\"future-guides-title\">\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">指南路线图</p>\n          <h2 id=\"future-guides-title\">回收设备购买者的未来指南主题</h2>\n          <p>这些指南主题将作为更深入的客户教育内容。在每篇文章建成之前，路线图会引导买家前往最近的 可用 资源。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"resource-guide-grid resource-guide-roadmap\">\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"resource-guide-status\">规划导游</span>\n            <h3>如何规划塑料回收分拣线</h3>\n            <p>PET、HDPE、PP和混合塑料项目的投入品、分拣类别、产能目标及提案详情。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/ai-optical-sorting-system-brochure\">从AI分拣手册开始</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"resource-guide-status\">规划导游</span>\n            <h3>如何评估C&D 废弃物回收厂</h3>\n            <p>C&amp;D废物项目的废物组成、工艺模块、输出产品、占地面积及场地状况。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/construction-waste-recycling-line-brochure\">从C&amp;D宣传册开始</a>\n          </article>\n          <article>\n            <span class=\"resource-guide-status\">可用 现在</span>\n            <h3>在申请回收设备报价前应准备哪些事项</h3>\n            <p>买方方的RFQ信息帮助供应商工程团队推荐更好的系统配置。</p>\n            <a class=\"resource-path-link\" href=\"/resources/project-inquiry-checklist\">开放调查清单</a>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"resources-contact-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">需要文件包吗？</p>\n          <h2 id=\"resources-contact-title\">请告诉我们你们团队正在评估什么</h2>\n          <p>分享你的项目阶段、物料流和文档需求。WEI LAN可以为您准备最相关的宣传册、参数摘要、常见问题解答和参考资料。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-contact-panel compact-contact-panel\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">请求资源包</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/case-studies\">评论参考文献</a>\n          <p>销售热线：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
